headline: Eli Lilly's Landmark Trial Shows Major Psoriasis-Obesity Breakthrough With Taltz-Zepbound Combo
summary: Eli Lilly and Co. (NYSE:LLY) on Wednesday shared topline results from the landmark TOGETHER-PsO open-label Phase 3b trial evaluating the concomitant use of Taltz (ixekizumab) and Zepbound (tirzepatide) compared to Taltz alone for plaque psoriasis and obesity.
